Create a new Page  You can manually create content files,
(for example as content/&lt;CATEGORY&gt;/&lt;FILE&gt;.&lt;FORMAT&gt;) and provide metadata in them, however you can use the new command to do a few things for you
(like add title and date): hugo new /&lt;CATEGORY&gt;/&lt;FILE&gt;.&lt;FORMAT&gt;
